Fit Yocto Board Support Package for iMX6
========================================

The 'setup-environment' script in this directory simplifies setup of
build environments.

To create a build directory, configure it for a specified machine and
distro, and prepare the calling shell for running bitbake, use the
script like this..

$ MACHINE=<machine name> DISTRO=<distro name> source setup-environment <build-dir>

To prepare the calling shell for running bitbake in an existing build
directory, use thie script like this..

$ source setup-environment <build-dir>

To show usage including supported machines and distros, do this..

$ source setup-environment

